    "description": "Rita began her journey into Ayurveda two decades ago when she was diagnosed with Crohn’s disease. Despite consulting with many specialists and doctors, Western medicine failed to yield a proper cure, and the disease took a debilitating toll on Rita’s career in the fashion industry, as well as her day to day life. After years studying health care, the drug industry and studying Ayurveda with Deepak Chopra, Rita opened the Ayurvedic Wellness Centre in Bondi Junction in 2011. The Ayurvedic Wellness Centre has become the preferred establishment in natural and holistic healing. With the warmth, compassion and expertise of our highly trained staff, we offer a truly authentic experience, restoring internal equilibrium, balance and well-being for the mind, body and soul.",
